  "decision_conditions": [
    "FORMAL DECISION  The Planning Inspectorate allow the appeal and grant planning permission for extension at roof level to provide new kitchen/dining room and roof terrace; new balcony at rear first floor level at 27A Wharfdale Road, London, N1 9SD in accordance with the terms of the application reference P032454, dated 11th November 2003 and the plans submitted therewith as subsequently amended, subject to the following conditions:\r\n\r\n1)  the development hereby permitted shall begin before the expiration of five years from the date of this decision;\r\n\r\n2)  notwithstanding the drawings hereby approved, no works shall take place on the respective parts of the development until full detailed drawings of the rear elevation of the proposed roof extension and the new doors to the proposed balcony at a scale of 1:50 have been submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority.  development shall be carried out in accordance with the approved details.\r\n\r\n3)  No works shall take place on the respective parts of the development until details of the facing materials to be used including railings/balustrades and screens have been submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority.  Development shall be carried out in accordance with the approved details."
